        <type name="Integer"/>
        <text>This gets set to the last error/warning number generated.

Can be used by specific trx's to return a code (should be an error constant)
which has specific meaning to the calling method (e.g to allow
display of a specfic message box ie. "System alerts have been generated,
do you want to display the System Alerts window now? (Yes/No)")</text>
    </PrimAttribute>
